WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 7=

00:01:49.210 --> 00:01:50.420 line:80%
You haven't rested well lately.

00:01:51.210 --> 00:01:52.050 line:80%
Today,

00:01:52.460 --> 00:01:53.540 line:80%
you should rest easy.

00:01:56.370 --> 00:01:58.260 line:80%
You usually do housework?

00:01:59.730 --> 00:02:02.060 line:80%
Just some small chores.

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:05.260 line:80%
I thought the Young Master
of the demon sect

00:02:06.010 --> 00:02:07.650 line:80%
lived in luxury,

00:02:07.730 --> 00:02:08.690 line:80%
with servants

00:02:09.140 --> 00:02:10.460 line:80%
at his beck and call.

00:02:10.740 --> 00:02:11.793 line:80%
You read it in a storybook?

00:02:13.530 --> 00:02:14.620 line:80%
Father doesn't like noise.

00:02:16.210 --> 00:02:17.490 line:80%
He told me

00:02:18.060 --> 00:02:19.460 line:80%
that cleaning every inch

00:02:19.810 --> 00:02:21.180 line:80%
of his room

00:02:21.650 --> 00:02:22.690 line:80%
and organizing every book

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:23.900 line:80%
he's read

00:02:24.530 --> 00:02:25.370 line:80%
was immensely joyful.

00:02:25.780 --> 00:02:26.620 line:80%
Your father is

00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:30.020 line:80%
not quite the man

00:02:30.020 --> 00:02:30.860 line:80%
I imagined.

00:02:33.210 --> 00:02:34.970 line:80%
In the stories,

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:36.860 line:80%
all the Mus

00:02:37.090 --> 00:02:38.620 line:80%
are bloodthirsty villains.

00:02:44.810 --> 00:02:45.650 line:80%
Where's Qian Xueshen?

00:02:45.990 --> 00:02:46.830 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:48.200 line:80%
He has a whole group serving him.

00:02:48.780 --> 00:02:49.930 line:80%
Right now,

00:02:50.180 --> 00:02:51.340 line:80%
it should be quite lively.

00:02:56.650 --> 00:02:57.490 line:80%
We're both guests.

00:02:57.740 --> 00:02:59.060 line:80%
Why is the treatment so different?

00:03:03.580 --> 00:03:04.420 line:80%
Mu,

00:03:04.900 --> 00:03:06.340 line:80%
how can you treat me like this?

00:03:08.690 --> 00:03:09.783 line:80%
The journey through the snow

00:03:09.896 --> 00:03:11.620 line:80%
is not as simple
as walking down the street

00:03:11.620 --> 00:03:13.060 line:80%
to buy a box of rouge.

00:03:14.740 --> 00:03:15.740 line:80%
This lawless land

00:03:16.410 --> 00:03:17.250 line:80%
has fierce customs.

00:03:17.810 --> 00:03:18.650 line:80%
It's very dangerous.

00:03:18.970 --> 00:03:20.740 line:80%
One misstep could lead to a trap.

00:03:21.020 --> 00:03:22.180 line:80%
This place is so dangerous.

00:03:22.530 --> 00:03:23.370 line:80%
I think

00:03:24.250 --> 00:03:25.340 line:80%
I should go with you.

00:03:25.740 --> 00:03:26.580 line:80%
Lately,

00:03:27.060 --> 00:03:29.530 line:80%
you've risked enough for me.

00:03:30.340 --> 00:03:31.180 line:80%
Besides,

00:03:31.410 --> 00:03:33.650 line:80%
isn't Nie Zhe clearing out
the Mu remnants?

00:03:33.930 --> 00:03:35.140 line:80%
You'd better stay out of sight.

00:03:37.650 --> 00:03:38.690 line:80%
Zhao, are you worried

00:03:39.690 --> 00:03:40.530 line:80%
about me?

00:03:42.020 --> 00:03:43.900 line:80%
I just think Nie Zhe is detestable.

00:03:46.090 --> 00:03:46.930 line:80%
By the way,

00:03:50.860 --> 00:03:52.340 line:80%
why did your Li Sect end up

00:03:52.580 --> 00:03:54.210 line:80%
with the Nie clan?

00:03:56.140 --> 00:03:58.180 line:80%
My great-grandfather
adopted Nie Hengcheng.

00:03:58.746 --> 00:04:00.060 line:80%
He later assisted my grandfather.

00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:01.293 line:80%
Grandfather died young.

00:04:01.620 --> 00:04:03.460 line:80%
At that time, Father was not yet ten,

00:04:04.020 --> 00:04:05.930 line:80%
so Nie Hengcheng took over the sect

00:04:06.420 --> 00:04:07.410 line:80%
until Father came of age.

00:04:08.180 --> 00:04:09.930 line:80%
But Father had no interest in power,

00:04:10.490 --> 00:04:12.340 line:80%
so Nie Hengcheng kept running the sect,

00:04:12.970 --> 00:04:15.140 line:80%
eventually taking it as his own.

00:04:16.090 --> 00:04:18.170 line:80%
What kind of person is Nie Hengcheng

00:04:19.140 --> 00:04:20.090 line:80%
that my aunt

00:04:20.850 --> 00:04:22.260 line:80%
would risk her life to kill him?

00:04:22.900 --> 00:04:24.090 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng is talented

00:04:24.260 --> 00:04:25.179 line:80%
and rare in the world.

00:04:25.970 --> 00:04:27.410 line:80%
To the Six Sects,

00:04:27.460 --> 00:04:28.610 line:80%
he's a demon.

00:04:29.380 --> 00:04:30.260 line:80%
But in our sect,

00:04:31.140 --> 00:04:32.530 line:80%
he is a pillar of the world,

00:04:33.380 --> 00:04:34.290 line:80%
an unshakable anchor.

00:04:36.340 --> 00:04:37.260 line:80%
Then why did he

00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:38.730 line:80%
go against all rules,

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:39.846 line:80%
killing without restraint?

00:04:40.340 --> 00:04:41.580 line:80%
That's because later

00:04:41.650 --> 00:04:43.340 line:80%
he mastered a supreme skill

00:04:46.340 --> 00:04:48.050 line:80%
that was called the Ziwei Method

00:04:48.260 --> 00:04:49.730 line:80%
and was created by the Mu ancestors.

00:04:50.260 --> 00:04:51.500 line:80%
This method

00:04:51.580 --> 00:04:52.530 line:80%
was powerful

00:04:52.530 --> 00:04:53.580 line:80%
and invincible,

00:04:54.290 --> 00:04:55.500 line:80%
but long lost.

00:04:55.610 --> 00:04:57.059 line:80%
Later, Nie Hengcheng somehow acquired

00:04:57.070 --> 00:04:58.290 line:80%
its cultivation method,

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:00.340 line:80%
and it became the root of all disasters.

00:05:00.410 --> 00:05:02.050 line:80%
Father told me about this skill.

00:05:02.460 --> 00:05:03.820 line:80%
He said such a defiant skill

00:05:04.140 --> 00:05:05.210 line:80%
must have hidden dangers;

00:05:05.419 --> 00:05:06.599 line:80%
better not to practice at all.

00:05:08.650 --> 00:05:10.380 line:80%
Your father is
truly a man of detachment.

00:05:11.260 --> 00:05:12.100 line:80%
I've always wondered:

00:05:13.340 --> 00:05:14.730 line:80%
If Father weren't so detached

00:05:15.900 --> 00:05:18.020 line:80%
and hadn't handed over
the Chief position,

00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:20.110 line:80%
how many lives

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:21.140 line:80%
would have changed?

00:05:22.380 --> 00:05:24.260 line:80%
Wu Yuanying wouldn't have suffered

00:05:24.260 --> 00:05:25.380 line:80%
for ten years.

00:05:26.850 --> 00:05:27.900 line:80%
Ms. Cai Pingshu

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:29.650 line:80%
wouldn't have died so early.

00:05:31.050 --> 00:05:32.210 line:80%
It's not his fault.

00:05:34.700 --> 00:05:36.610 line:80%
He simply didn't want to go
against his heart.

00:05:37.290 --> 00:05:38.340 line:80%
My aunt was like that, too.

00:05:39.780 --> 00:05:41.050 line:80%
She was bold and fearless

00:05:42.260 --> 00:05:45.210 line:80%
but afraid of being trapped at home.

00:05:46.340 --> 00:05:47.730 line:80%
Perhaps the same applies

00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:49.180 line:80%
to your father.

00:05:50.340 --> 00:05:51.180 line:80%
Your father

00:05:51.500 --> 00:05:52.850 line:80%
must be a very good man.

00:05:53.650 --> 00:05:54.580 line:80%
Otherwise, Uncle Chang

00:05:54.580 --> 00:05:57.006 line:80%
wouldn't trust you so easily
after a single act of kindness.

00:05:57.730 --> 00:05:59.076 line:80%
It must be because of your father

00:05:59.460 --> 00:06:00.610 line:80%
that he believes

00:06:01.610 --> 00:06:02.576 line:80%
you're not a bad person.

00:06:04.780 --> 00:06:05.620 line:80%
Zhao...

00:06:12.050 --> 00:06:12.890 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:06:35.020 --> 00:06:35.860 line:80%
Thank you.

00:06:56.460 --> 00:06:57.933 line:80%
(Uncle Cheng, Li Sect)
Young Master,

00:06:57.944 --> 00:06:59.689 line:80%
you weren't affected
by the sleeping powder,

00:06:59.700 --> 00:07:01.850 line:80%
so why let Miss Cai go?

00:07:06.170 --> 00:07:07.380 line:80%
To cheer her up.

00:07:45.460 --> 00:07:46.410 line:80%
What a worthless bird.

00:07:46.820 --> 00:07:48.066 line:80%
It probably follows its master.

00:07:50.580 --> 00:07:51.900 line:80%
It's about to snow.

00:07:52.580 --> 00:07:53.700 line:80%
This place is so remote.

00:07:54.580 --> 00:07:56.050 line:80%
Is there somewhere to stay?

00:08:40.570 --> 00:08:41.410 line:80%
Ma'am,

00:08:41.450 --> 00:08:42.500 line:80%
we're here to stay.

00:08:44.860 --> 00:08:45.930 line:80%
Miss,

00:08:46.570 --> 00:08:47.500 line:80%
may I ask your name?

00:08:49.450 --> 00:08:50.290 line:80%
I'm Feng Xiaohan.

00:08:50.570 --> 00:08:51.900 line:80%
This is my...

00:08:52.410 --> 00:08:53.250 line:80%
Well.

00:08:53.450 --> 00:08:54.780 line:80%
My fiancé,

00:08:55.450 --> 00:08:56.290 line:80%
Wan Dazhuang.

00:08:56.450 --> 00:08:57.290 line:80%
Wan...

00:08:59.100 --> 00:09:00.380 line:80%
Since you two are a couple,

00:09:03.380 --> 00:09:04.380 line:80%
Blooming Flowers

00:09:04.570 --> 00:09:06.140 line:80%
is our best room.

00:09:06.410 --> 00:09:07.650 line:80%
It has a soft animal-skin bed

00:09:07.650 --> 00:09:08.500 line:80%
and fine bedding,

00:09:08.930 --> 00:09:10.470 line:80%
and the back door leads to hot springs.

00:09:10.650 --> 00:09:11.530 line:80%
Very romantic.

00:09:12.220 --> 00:09:13.220 line:80%
Payment

00:09:14.100 --> 00:09:14.980 line:80%
can be settled later

00:09:15.380 --> 00:09:17.020 line:80%
at checkout.

00:09:18.410 --> 00:09:20.100 line:80%
I didn't expect such attentive service

00:09:20.330 --> 00:09:22.140 line:80%
(Blooming Flowers)
in this harsh, cold land.

00:09:22.290 --> 00:09:23.860 line:80%
Right, Dazhuang?

00:09:27.330 --> 00:09:28.810 line:80%
I'll bring your meal first.

00:09:30.330 --> 00:09:31.860 line:80%
You two look young

00:09:32.170 --> 00:09:33.100 line:80%
and delicate.

00:09:33.450 --> 00:09:35.140 line:80%
Why come to this freezing place?

00:09:38.260 --> 00:09:40.050 line:80%
To see the snowy scenery.

00:09:40.380 --> 00:09:41.220 line:80%
See the scenery?

00:09:41.780 --> 00:09:43.220 line:80%
This blizzard

00:09:43.810 --> 00:09:45.690 line:80%
is hardly a good time to sightsee.

00:09:45.780 --> 00:09:46.620 line:80%
Is that so?

00:09:49.690 --> 00:09:51.380 line:80%
I'll set the dishes for you.

00:09:52.650 --> 00:09:53.570 line:80%
Thanks, ma'am.

00:09:55.860 --> 00:09:57.330 line:80%
It's too hot!

00:09:59.690 --> 00:10:00.530 line:80%
Sorry.

00:10:00.530 --> 00:10:01.370 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:10:01.690 --> 00:10:02.570 line:80%
Sorry to disturb you.

00:10:03.170 --> 00:10:04.020 line:80%
Sorry.

00:10:04.050 --> 00:10:04.890 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:10:06.290 --> 00:10:07.130 line:80%
Sorry.

00:10:07.380 --> 00:10:08.260 line:80%
Sorry to disturb you.

00:10:08.690 --> 00:10:10.020 line:80%
I'm too clumsy.

00:10:12.170 --> 00:10:13.900 line:80%
(Qinong)
Are you also here for the saliva?

00:10:14.930 --> 00:10:15.900 line:80%
What saliva?

00:10:16.650 --> 00:10:18.740 line:80%
The saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

00:10:19.220 --> 00:10:21.530 line:80%
It's said the long-lost Snow-Scale Beast

00:10:21.530 --> 00:10:22.860 line:80%
is about to appear.

00:10:23.410 --> 00:10:25.410 line:80%
Its saliva can repair internal energy

00:10:25.410 --> 00:10:26.330 line:80%
and grant longevity.

00:10:26.740 --> 00:10:27.980 line:80%
My master is weak,

00:10:28.450 --> 00:10:30.170 line:80%
so we're hoping for some luck.

00:10:30.500 --> 00:10:31.780 line:80%
Qinong.

00:10:32.410 --> 00:10:33.530 line:80%
I need to go back.

00:10:44.570 --> 00:10:45.410 line:80%
Slow down.

00:10:45.620 --> 00:10:46.460 line:80%
Wan Dazhuang?

00:10:48.170 --> 00:10:49.260 line:80%
Eyes frozen

00:10:49.260 --> 00:10:50.140 line:80%
on the beauty?

00:11:03.140 --> 00:11:04.050 line:80%
Miss,

00:11:04.900 --> 00:11:06.410 line:80%
this place isn't safe.

00:11:06.900 --> 00:11:08.290 line:80%
Do you want us

00:11:08.530 --> 00:11:09.650 line:80%
to scout the path?

00:11:10.020 --> 00:11:10.980 line:80%
Go away!

00:11:39.330 --> 00:11:40.170 line:80%
You...

00:11:41.260 --> 00:11:42.100 line:80%
It wasn't me.

00:11:44.860 --> 00:11:45.700 line:80%
It was me.

00:12:15.860 --> 00:12:17.330 line:80%
I've looked for you for so long.

00:12:23.410 --> 00:12:24.650 line:80%
Why betray me

00:12:24.810 --> 00:12:26.050 line:80%
and elope with this pretty boy?

00:12:29.380 --> 00:12:30.260 line:80%
Sir,

00:12:30.740 --> 00:12:32.410 line:80%
your attack is so cruel.

00:12:32.900 --> 00:12:34.780 line:80%
Though their behavior was wrong,

00:12:34.980 --> 00:12:36.140 line:80%
they didn't deserve death.

00:12:38.620 --> 00:12:39.460 line:80%
You...

00:12:45.690 --> 00:12:46.530 line:80%
Everyone,

00:12:48.650 --> 00:12:51.650 line:80%
those two are notorious rapists
in the northwest,

00:12:51.980 --> 00:12:53.993 line:80%
killing dozens of women.

00:12:54.004 --> 00:12:55.169 line:80%
(Zhou Zhiqin, Peiqiong Manor)

00:12:55.180 --> 00:12:56.290 line:80%
They deserved

00:12:57.020 --> 00:12:58.380 line:80%
such deaths.

00:12:59.500 --> 00:13:01.570 line:80%
This is Uncle Zhou's cousin.

00:13:02.020 --> 00:13:03.290 line:80%
I saw him as a child.

00:13:05.290 --> 00:13:07.260 line:80%
Are you from Peiqiong Manor?

00:13:08.260 --> 00:13:09.650 line:80%
I'm Zhou Zhiqin.

00:13:11.020 --> 00:13:12.100 line:80%
May I ask

00:13:12.810 --> 00:13:13.900 line:80%
your name?

00:13:14.330 --> 00:13:15.220 line:80%
I am

00:13:16.900 --> 00:13:17.740 line:80%
Yan Ning.

00:13:18.780 --> 00:13:20.410 line:80%
Thanks for your help, Mr. Zhou.

00:13:25.380 --> 00:13:26.780 line:80%
You're my fiancée,

00:13:27.740 --> 00:13:29.290 line:80%
yet you ran off with my heirloom

00:13:29.740 --> 00:13:31.620 line:80%
and this pretty boy.

00:13:31.980 --> 00:13:33.020 line:80%
Surely, I'd look for you.

00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:35.170 line:80%
Who took your heirloom?

00:13:35.170 --> 00:13:36.980 line:80%
Wait. Who is your fiancée?

00:13:37.050 --> 00:13:38.810 line:80%
I'm not the pretty boy either.

00:13:40.380 --> 00:13:42.050 line:80%
Isn't this my heirloom,

00:13:42.050 --> 00:13:43.740 line:80%
the scale of the Snow-Scale Beast?

00:13:47.620 --> 00:13:48.500 line:80%
What a pity.

00:13:48.810 --> 00:13:50.690 line:80%
The pretty boy defiled it.

00:13:53.380 --> 00:13:54.346 line:80%
I don't want it anymore.

00:13:58.490 --> 00:13:59.340 line:80%
I want it.

00:13:59.850 --> 00:14:00.710 line:80%
Give it to me!

00:14:00.930 --> 00:14:01.990 line:80%
Mine!

00:14:02.410 --> 00:14:03.350 line:80%
Mine!

00:14:05.780 --> 00:14:06.650 line:80%
Played enough?

00:14:08.650 --> 00:14:10.050 line:80%
Just some Jianghu punks.

00:14:10.860 --> 00:14:12.530 line:80%
They can hardly fight.

00:14:12.900 --> 00:14:14.050 line:80%
Except for Mr. Zhou,

00:14:14.500 --> 00:14:15.500 line:80%
they're nothing.

00:14:16.810 --> 00:14:19.330 line:80%
Those three haven't acted yet.

00:14:28.290 --> 00:14:30.620 line:80%
Why did your Uncle Zhou
also want the scale?

00:14:31.330 --> 00:14:32.380 line:80%
I don't know.

00:14:32.980 --> 00:14:34.170 line:80%
This is enough.

00:14:41.690 --> 00:14:43.140 line:80%
No wonder it's a family heirloom.

00:14:43.170 --> 00:14:45.530 line:80%
I heard the Snow-Scale Beast
can sense this scale.

00:14:46.450 --> 00:14:47.500 line:80%
Losing it would be a shame.

00:14:49.100 --> 00:14:50.140 line:80%
Why not lend it to me?

00:14:51.330 --> 00:14:53.780 line:80%
Dazhuang has been weak since childhood.

00:14:54.140 --> 00:14:55.559 line:80%
I want to secure the saliva for him.

00:14:56.810 --> 00:14:58.690 line:80%
So, it is for the pretty boy.

00:15:04.780 --> 00:15:05.620 line:80%
Mr. Yan,

00:15:06.170 --> 00:15:07.980 line:80%
my son had an accident here last year.

00:15:09.330 --> 00:15:10.650 line:80%
The guards who escaped said

00:15:11.410 --> 00:15:13.220 line:80%
he encountered the Snow-Scale Beast

00:15:13.500 --> 00:15:14.340 line:80%
and died.

00:15:15.260 --> 00:15:16.980 line:80%
I just want to retrieve his body

00:15:17.220 --> 00:15:18.220 line:80%
for a proper burial.

00:15:19.290 --> 00:15:20.500 line:80%
Please, Mr. Yan,

00:15:21.140 --> 00:15:22.050 line:80%
lend me the scale.

00:15:23.100 --> 00:15:23.990 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:25.490 line:80%
- Give it to me.
- Mr. Yan.

00:15:25.650 --> 00:15:26.490 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:15:27.173 --> 00:15:28.548 line:80%
- Give it to me.
- I need it, too.

00:15:28.559 --> 00:15:29.340 line:80%
Mr. Yan.

00:15:30.500 --> 00:15:31.340 line:80%
Good.

00:15:31.780 --> 00:15:32.930 line:80%
Once we find the saliva,

00:15:33.530 --> 00:15:35.050 line:80%
you'll come back with me.

00:15:36.810 --> 00:15:37.810 line:80%
Tomorrow morning,

00:15:38.140 --> 00:15:39.450 line:80%
let's set off

00:15:40.260 --> 00:15:41.620 line:80%
to find the saliva.

00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:43.020 line:80%
Okay.

00:15:47.740 --> 00:15:50.100 line:80%
Where did you get the scale?

00:15:51.100 --> 00:15:52.020 line:80%
The Jiuzhou Archive.

00:15:53.980 --> 00:15:55.020 line:80%
Does it have slime?

00:15:55.220 --> 00:15:56.380 line:80%
That kind of substance

00:15:56.650 --> 00:15:57.756 line:80%
does not congeal in the cold

00:15:57.860 --> 00:15:58.780 line:80%
and melts when heated.

00:15:59.620 --> 00:16:01.260 line:80%
The archive
hasn't been cleaned for ages.

00:16:01.450 --> 00:16:02.643 line:80%
So, it couldn't be preserved.

00:16:03.476 --> 00:16:04.889 line:80%
Are we really going up the mountain

00:16:04.900 --> 00:16:06.170 line:80%
with those people tomorrow?

00:16:06.500 --> 00:16:07.773 line:80%
The enemy is better in the open

00:16:07.980 --> 00:16:08.980 line:80%
than in the dark.

00:16:11.740 --> 00:16:13.290 line:80%
Why did you chase after us?

00:16:15.930 --> 00:16:17.740 line:80%
You stole my Peng.

00:16:18.523 --> 00:16:19.810 line:80%
Of course, I had to get it back.

00:16:24.530 --> 00:16:25.370 line:80%
Sleeping powder?

00:16:47.900 --> 00:16:48.810 line:80%
The landlady?

00:16:49.930 --> 00:16:51.450 line:80%
Why sneak in

00:16:51.860 --> 00:16:52.860 line:80%
at night?

00:16:54.100 --> 00:16:55.360 line:80%
The snow mountains have spirits.

00:16:55.740 --> 00:16:57.170 line:80%
Trespassers won't fare well.

00:16:57.620 --> 00:16:58.500 line:80%
I advise you two

00:16:58.650 --> 00:16:59.690 line:80%
to return the way you came

00:17:00.330 --> 00:17:01.900 line:80%
to save your lives.

00:17:03.100 --> 00:17:04.173 line:80%
You must be very familiar

00:17:04.420 --> 00:17:06.090 line:80%
with the snowy mountains.

00:17:06.700 --> 00:17:07.540 line:80%
Better stay

00:17:07.980 --> 00:17:08.940 line:80%
and guide us.

00:17:19.220 --> 00:17:20.500 line:80%
Hidden elites.

00:17:21.420 --> 00:17:22.260 line:80%
Interesting.

00:17:52.050 --> 00:17:53.020 line:80%
You're still sick.

00:17:53.660 --> 00:17:54.530 line:80%
Why come here?

00:17:58.740 --> 00:18:00.166 line:80%
Are you worried about that Cai girl?

00:18:01.032 --> 00:18:02.502 line:80%
If not for fearing I'd slow her down,

00:18:03.330 --> 00:18:04.420 line:80%
I would go with her.

00:18:06.370 --> 00:18:08.610 line:80%
Zhao is not simple.

00:18:09.330 --> 00:18:11.700 line:80%
She might bring back the antidote.

00:18:12.020 --> 00:18:12.860 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:18:13.420 --> 00:18:16.290 line:80%
you've never seemed to care
so much about Lingbo.

00:18:18.660 --> 00:18:19.610 line:80%
Master is in danger;

00:18:20.090 --> 00:18:21.330 line:80%
the sect is in peril.

00:18:21.850 --> 00:18:23.260 line:80%
Yet you still have time for jokes?

00:18:25.180 --> 00:18:26.090 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:18:26.460 --> 00:18:27.300 line:80%
With me here,

00:18:28.220 --> 00:18:30.330 line:80%
Qingque Sect won't fall into chaos.

00:19:44.330 --> 00:19:45.740 line:80%
I'm still here.

00:20:10.020 --> 00:20:11.220 line:80%
There's not even a direction.

00:20:11.700 --> 00:20:12.890 line:80%
Where do we start looking?

00:20:13.370 --> 00:20:14.260 line:80%
Elder Tianji,

00:20:15.980 --> 00:20:17.130 line:80%
let's find a place to rest.

00:20:17.530 --> 00:20:18.370 line:80%
Alright.

00:20:19.020 --> 00:20:21.090 line:80%
Everyone, rest up ahead.

00:20:21.500 --> 00:20:22.340 line:80%
Let's go.

00:20:30.330 --> 00:20:31.170 line:80%
Qian Xueshen,

00:20:31.500 --> 00:20:32.850 line:80%
why so quiet today?

00:20:33.290 --> 00:20:34.810 line:80%
That's unusual.

00:20:38.700 --> 00:20:39.940 line:80%
Where's Mr. Zhang trailing us?

00:20:40.330 --> 00:20:41.260 line:80%
Who saw him?

00:20:48.500 --> 00:20:49.340 line:80%
Something's wrong.

00:20:50.290 --> 00:20:51.370 line:80%
We just came this way.

00:20:51.700 --> 00:20:52.890 line:80%
I've seen this stone.

00:20:53.330 --> 00:20:54.530 line:80%
We're back here again.

00:20:56.370 --> 00:20:57.260 line:80%
A ghost maze?

00:21:00.740 --> 00:21:01.940 line:80%
What a mess.

00:21:02.020 --> 00:21:03.020 line:80%
When we first came here,

00:21:03.220 --> 00:21:04.060 line:80%
we went straight...

00:21:07.460 --> 00:21:08.300 line:80%
It's a maze.

00:21:08.530 --> 00:21:09.730 line:80%
Everyone, line up,

00:21:09.810 --> 00:21:10.650 line:80%
one after another.

00:21:11.050 --> 00:21:12.020 line:80%
Try not to get separated.

00:21:12.500 --> 00:21:13.660 line:80%
This...

00:21:13.660 --> 00:21:14.510 line:80%
It's getting dark.

00:21:14.520 --> 00:21:16.220 line:80%
With a ghost maze, we'll never get out.

00:21:17.180 --> 00:21:18.500 line:80%
We'll either freeze

00:21:18.500 --> 00:21:19.610 line:80%
or starve to death here.

00:21:31.080 --> 00:21:32.519 line:80%
Where there's a will, there's a way.

00:21:32.530 --> 00:21:33.530 line:80%
As long as we follow it,

00:21:33.570 --> 00:21:34.700 line:80%
we can escape the maze.

00:21:34.890 --> 00:21:35.730 line:80%
Move.

00:21:37.020 --> 00:21:37.860 line:80%
Come on.

00:21:45.330 --> 00:21:46.810 line:80%
Unordinary fingers.

00:21:47.090 --> 00:21:47.940 line:80%
He knows palm kills

00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:52.700 line:80%
and can break the ice with inner power

00:21:53.090 --> 00:21:54.050 line:80%
to break the maze.

00:21:55.220 --> 00:21:56.500 line:80%
Who is he?

00:22:03.180 --> 00:22:04.020 line:80%
There's a house.

00:22:04.510 --> 00:22:06.039 line:80%
Everyone, get inside to avoid the snow.

00:22:06.050 --> 00:22:06.890 line:80%
Let's go.

00:22:16.180 --> 00:22:17.020 line:80%
Hurry.

00:22:17.220 --> 00:22:18.060 line:80%
Come on.

00:22:19.850 --> 00:22:20.690 line:80%
Follow closely.

00:22:39.050 --> 00:22:40.740 line:80%
This place has been abandoned for years.

00:22:53.700 --> 00:22:54.700 line:80%
Shu?

00:23:00.610 --> 00:23:01.570 line:80%
You two,

00:23:02.020 --> 00:23:03.740 line:80%
find a place to sleep.

00:23:44.810 --> 00:23:46.180 line:80%
Time to eat.

00:23:48.700 --> 00:23:50.420 line:80%
He's truly exhausted.

00:24:01.020 --> 00:24:01.980 line:80%
He won't get cold.

00:24:10.020 --> 00:24:11.130 line:80%
This trip

00:24:11.700 --> 00:24:13.020 line:80%
is undoubtedly perilous.

00:24:13.940 --> 00:24:15.460 line:80%
Are you really going to accompany me?

00:24:19.050 --> 00:24:20.460 line:80%
Though you're heartless toward me,

00:24:22.290 --> 00:24:23.700 line:80%
I can't do the same to you.

00:24:38.460 --> 00:24:39.610 line:80%
That old servant

00:24:40.940 --> 00:24:42.420 line:80%
reminds me of someone.

00:24:45.420 --> 00:24:46.260 line:80%
Who?

00:24:46.610 --> 00:24:48.396 line:80%
Another adopted son
of my great-grandfather,

00:24:49.130 --> 00:24:50.180 line:80%
Elder Tianji,

00:24:50.570 --> 00:24:51.410 line:80%
Duan Jiuxiu.

00:24:53.780 --> 00:24:55.330 line:80%
He and Nie Hengcheng were both adopted.

00:24:56.090 --> 00:24:57.780 line:80%
Why was Nie Hengcheng the Chief,

00:24:58.500 --> 00:24:59.613 line:80%
while he was just an elder?

00:25:01.090 --> 00:25:02.260 line:80%
So, he couldn't accept it.

00:25:03.850 --> 00:25:06.050 line:80%
16 years ago,
the Lord of Qingfeng Temple

00:25:06.220 --> 00:25:07.780 line:80%
mocked him as the eternal second.

00:25:08.220 --> 00:25:09.940 line:80%
He slaughtered the entire temple

00:25:10.850 --> 00:25:12.460 line:80%
and even turned young novices under ten

00:25:13.180 --> 00:25:14.420 line:80%
into human fodder.

00:25:19.780 --> 00:25:22.220 line:80%
Later, your aunt issued a Death Warrant.

00:25:22.760 --> 00:25:23.610 line:80%
It's said

00:25:23.610 --> 00:25:25.420 line:80%
he died in a ruined temple.

00:25:40.740 --> 00:25:42.460 line:80%
The footprint of the Snow-Scale Beast.

00:25:45.740 --> 00:25:46.700 line:80%
Congratulations, Master.

00:25:46.700 --> 00:25:47.900 line:80%
Move, move!

00:25:48.980 --> 00:25:49.820 line:80%
Let's go!

00:26:03.370 --> 00:26:05.050 line:80%
It's the Jade Statue.

00:26:07.020 --> 00:26:08.610 line:80%
The flowers on the base look

00:26:09.050 --> 00:26:11.530 line:80%
like the tri-colored peach blossoms
unique to Luoying Valley.

00:26:13.020 --> 00:26:14.420 line:80%
Could she be Gu Qingkong?

00:26:14.780 --> 00:26:15.700 line:80%
In the wilderness,

00:26:16.020 --> 00:26:17.610 line:80%
who put this statue here?

00:27:01.570 --> 00:27:02.530 line:80%
All dead.

00:27:07.180 --> 00:27:08.290 line:80%
Dead for over six months.

00:27:14.460 --> 00:27:15.300 line:80%
There's a hole here.

00:27:15.680 --> 00:27:16.520 line:80%
A hole?

00:27:33.890 --> 00:27:34.730 line:80%
Wait.

00:27:37.370 --> 00:27:38.410 line:80%
There's something inside.

00:27:49.740 --> 00:27:50.610 line:80%
A snake!

00:27:50.610 --> 00:27:51.850 line:80%
A huge snake!

00:28:01.610 --> 00:28:02.980 line:80%
Qian Xueshen!

00:28:26.370 --> 00:28:27.500 line:80%
The Red-Eyed Crystal Python,

00:28:27.700 --> 00:28:28.540 line:80%
an ancient beast.

00:28:28.836 --> 00:28:30.432 line:80%
Its breath can connect to the underworld

00:28:30.443 --> 00:28:31.330 line:80%
and freeze everything.

00:28:31.500 --> 00:28:32.350 line:80%
Zhao,

00:28:32.370 --> 00:28:33.210 line:80%
stay close to me.

00:28:33.740 --> 00:28:34.580 line:80%
Alright.

00:28:39.050 --> 00:28:39.890 line:80%
Run!

00:28:45.180 --> 00:28:46.020 line:80%
Qian Xueshen!

00:29:17.980 --> 00:29:18.820 line:80%
Go!

00:29:46.256 --> 00:29:47.260 line:80%
I thought you'd care less

00:29:47.260 --> 00:29:48.530 line:80%
about life and death

00:29:49.050 --> 00:29:51.420 line:80%
after the Qingque Sect massacre.

00:29:52.740 --> 00:29:54.500 line:80%
Qian Xueshen came with me.

00:29:56.220 --> 00:29:57.330 line:80%
He's not evil.

00:29:57.890 --> 00:29:59.130 line:80%
If he falls into the hands

00:29:59.130 --> 00:30:00.020 line:80%
of the Demonic Camp,

00:30:00.290 --> 00:30:01.260 line:80%
after they use him,

00:30:01.980 --> 00:30:02.940 line:80%
he'll be dead anyway.

00:30:04.610 --> 00:30:05.780 line:80%
Jianghu is like this.

00:30:07.090 --> 00:30:08.780 line:80%
Only ruthlessness ensures survival.

00:30:09.980 --> 00:30:11.090 line:80%
If you're not ruthless,

00:30:12.610 --> 00:30:14.500 line:80%
you'll end up like Qian Xueshen.

00:30:16.220 --> 00:30:17.060 line:80%
Yulin,

00:30:18.260 --> 00:30:19.180 line:80%
I'm here.

00:30:20.180 --> 00:30:21.850 line:80%
I'll take you home.

00:30:34.260 --> 00:30:36.090 line:80%
That's Zhou Zhiqin's son, Zhou Yulin.

00:30:42.130 --> 00:30:42.970 line:80%
Yulin...

00:30:43.090 --> 00:30:45.130 line:80%
- Mr. Zhou found his son.
- Yulin.

00:30:52.660 --> 00:30:53.500 line:80%
That is...

00:30:54.220 --> 00:30:56.740 line:80%
(Mr. Zhou wants the saliva for himself.)

00:30:57.850 --> 00:30:58.690 line:80%
Jiu,

00:30:59.660 --> 00:31:01.260 line:80%
go help Mr. Zhou.

00:31:01.260 --> 00:31:02.100 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:11.260 --> 00:31:12.100 line:80%
Don't come near.

00:31:13.130 --> 00:31:14.180 line:80%
I don't need your help.

00:31:14.980 --> 00:31:16.290 line:80%
I'll take Yulin back myself.

00:31:17.570 --> 00:31:20.330 line:80%
Better let me help you.

00:31:52.290 --> 00:31:53.940 line:80%
Is this the Snow-Scale Beast's saliva?

00:31:54.660 --> 00:31:55.890 line:80%
Return it.

00:32:09.850 --> 00:32:10.690 line:80%
Mr. Zhou.

00:32:12.220 --> 00:32:13.060 line:80%
Mr. Zhou.

00:32:14.020 --> 00:32:15.330 line:80%
That belongs to Yulin.

00:32:16.050 --> 00:32:17.130 line:80%
Don't give it to him.

00:32:19.780 --> 00:32:20.850 line:80%
Take Mr. Zhou away.

00:32:21.519 --> 00:32:23.052 line:80%
We'll meet at the foot of the mountain.

00:32:23.940 --> 00:32:24.940 line:80%
I'll wait there for you.

00:32:39.370 --> 00:32:40.290 line:80%
Elder Tianji.

00:32:44.020 --> 00:32:45.090 line:80%
Kid.

00:32:45.500 --> 00:32:47.060 line:80%
(Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji)
Sharp eyes.

00:32:47.090 --> 00:32:48.850 line:80%
You recognized me.

00:32:51.210 --> 00:32:52.940 line:80%
You were once Elder Tianji,

00:32:53.980 --> 00:32:55.610 line:80%
but now you're reduced

00:32:56.500 --> 00:32:57.700 line:80%
to following behind,

00:32:57.940 --> 00:32:58.890 line:80%
acting as a servant.

00:32:59.290 --> 00:33:01.370 line:80%
Truly tragic.

00:33:02.180 --> 00:33:03.660 line:80%
You're asking for death.

00:33:07.890 --> 00:33:09.180 line:80%
I heard that one is the weakest

00:33:09.180 --> 00:33:10.530 line:80%
among Nie Hengcheng's

00:33:10.890 --> 00:33:12.290 line:80%
four disciples.

00:33:13.330 --> 00:33:15.700 line:80%
He survived only

00:33:16.610 --> 00:33:18.500 line:80%
by flattering Nie Zhe daily.

00:33:19.570 --> 00:33:20.410 line:80%
I think

00:33:20.940 --> 00:33:22.610 line:80%
it must be you, Chen Shu.

00:33:22.610 --> 00:33:24.610 line:80%
(Chen Shu, Li Sect)

00:33:24.610 --> 00:33:26.740 line:80%
You know too much.

00:33:26.890 --> 00:33:28.610 line:80%
I think you've grown tired of living.

00:33:28.610 --> 00:33:29.940 line:80%
Who are you?

00:33:30.660 --> 00:33:31.500 line:80%
Who am I?

00:33:31.850 --> 00:33:32.850 line:80%
I'm your ancestor.

00:33:38.460 --> 00:33:39.420 line:80%
Wudu Palm.

00:33:40.460 --> 00:33:41.980 line:80%
You recognize it.

00:33:42.570 --> 00:33:44.500 line:80%
You're of the Li Sect?

00:33:44.850 --> 00:33:46.020 line:80%
As a Li Sect member,

00:33:47.080 --> 00:33:48.530 line:80%
how dare you covet the Ziwei Method,

00:33:48.530 --> 00:33:49.420 line:80%
wanting to practice it?

00:33:50.810 --> 00:33:52.420 line:80%
If Nie Zhe knew,

00:33:53.050 --> 00:33:54.283 line:80%
your bones would be gouged out,

00:33:54.570 --> 00:33:55.610 line:80%
and you'd be beheaded.

00:33:56.020 --> 00:33:57.220 line:80%
How arrogant

00:33:57.220 --> 00:33:58.700 line:80%
before death.

00:34:15.060 --> 00:34:16.133 line:80%
(His skills are so strong.)

00:34:16.330 --> 00:34:17.620 line:80%
(He should be able to escape.)

00:34:18.930 --> 00:34:19.770 line:80%
No.

00:34:20.780 --> 00:34:21.740 line:80%
I must help him.

00:34:24.010 --> 00:34:24.850 line:80%
Miss Feng.

00:34:25.810 --> 00:34:26.740 line:80%
Miss Feng.

00:34:32.450 --> 00:34:33.290 line:80%
Mr. Zhou,

00:34:33.620 --> 00:34:34.460 line:80%
how are you?

00:34:38.540 --> 00:34:39.970 line:80%
Thanks to your medicine,

00:34:40.540 --> 00:34:41.380 line:80%
I'm much better.

00:34:41.660 --> 00:34:42.500 line:80%
Thank you.

00:34:43.700 --> 00:34:44.930 line:80%
Then rest a bit.

00:34:45.490 --> 00:34:47.060 line:80%
We'll leave first.

00:34:47.580 --> 00:34:49.410 line:80%
I, as a father, have failed.

00:34:50.100 --> 00:34:51.450 line:80%
I can't take my son home

00:34:51.890 --> 00:34:53.290 line:80%
and have to leave him alone

00:34:53.290 --> 00:34:55.010 line:80%
in this snow-covered mountain.

00:34:56.970 --> 00:34:58.810 line:80%
You must protect the saliva.

00:34:59.100 --> 00:35:02.780 line:80%
It's my son's last item for me.

00:35:06.200 --> 00:35:07.780 line:80%
Mr. Zhou, young lady,

00:35:07.780 --> 00:35:08.620 line:80%
you two are here.

00:35:08.780 --> 00:35:09.933 line:80%
We've looked for a long time.

00:35:10.140 --> 00:35:10.980 line:80%
Where are they?

00:35:14.180 --> 00:35:15.220 line:80%
Your lover

00:35:15.580 --> 00:35:16.420 line:80%
stubbornly refused

00:35:16.660 --> 00:35:17.500 line:80%
to leave

00:35:18.220 --> 00:35:19.220 line:80%
and was swallowed

00:35:19.930 --> 00:35:20.810 line:80%
by the python

00:35:22.580 --> 00:35:23.700 line:80%
with Jiu.

00:35:31.540 --> 00:35:32.450 line:80%
He's dead?

00:35:33.580 --> 00:35:35.010 line:80%
The python was too fierce.

00:35:35.330 --> 00:35:37.260 line:80%
Its icy breath killed him instantly.

00:35:37.890 --> 00:35:39.850 line:80%
What a pity for the cute young man.

00:35:40.620 --> 00:35:41.580 line:80%
My condolences.

00:35:48.410 --> 00:35:49.250 line:80%
Young lady,

00:35:50.490 --> 00:35:51.890 line:80%
you still have the saliva, right?

00:35:52.450 --> 00:35:53.970 line:80%
Jiu was wrong to take it,

00:35:54.260 --> 00:35:56.180 line:80%
but this saliva is vital to our master.

00:35:56.450 --> 00:35:58.260 line:80%
Now, it's useless for you.

00:35:58.620 --> 00:35:59.553 line:80%
Why not sell it to us?

00:36:00.060 --> 00:36:00.900 line:80%
Set a price.

00:36:01.700 --> 00:36:02.540 line:80%
A thousand gold?

00:36:02.740 --> 00:36:04.230 line:80%
Miss Feng, don't listen to them.

00:36:04.260 --> 00:36:05.100 line:80%
They are bad people.

00:36:05.620 --> 00:36:06.740 line:80%
Once we restrain them,

00:36:07.290 --> 00:36:08.436 line:80%
we'll go find your companion.

00:36:29.810 --> 00:36:30.740 line:80%
Sunshine Blade...

00:36:33.450 --> 00:36:34.330 line:80%
You are Cai Zhao?

00:36:34.890 --> 00:36:35.730 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:36:36.540 --> 00:36:37.450 line:80%
long time no see

00:36:37.780 --> 00:36:38.810 line:80%
since childhood.

00:36:39.180 --> 00:36:40.580 line:80%
How have you been?

00:36:41.100 --> 00:36:42.010 line:80%
Kid,

00:36:42.370 --> 00:36:43.850 line:80%
why attack me?

00:36:44.290 --> 00:36:46.060 line:80%
My aunt grew up in Peiqiong Manor

00:36:46.370 --> 00:36:47.210 line:80%
and could recognize

00:36:47.580 --> 00:36:49.013 line:80%
the Zhous' swordsmanship blindfolded.

00:36:49.740 --> 00:36:50.890 line:80%
I don't have eyes on my back,

00:36:51.540 --> 00:36:52.930 line:80%
but I saw your shadow.

00:36:53.890 --> 00:36:55.100 line:80%
Your sword

00:36:55.620 --> 00:36:57.580 line:80%
is in the Moonlight Drinking stance,

00:36:58.290 --> 00:37:00.330 line:80%
a close combat technique.

00:37:01.490 --> 00:37:03.060 line:80%
They were so far apart.

00:37:03.740 --> 00:37:04.580 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:37:05.540 --> 00:37:07.290 line:80%
who exactly are you trying to kill?

00:37:08.140 --> 00:37:09.010 line:80%
Actually, I...

00:37:09.010 --> 00:37:09.970 line:80%
I felt it was strange

00:37:10.660 --> 00:37:11.780 line:80%
in the ice cave.

00:37:12.060 --> 00:37:13.260 line:80%
Seeing the corpse of your kin,

00:37:13.580 --> 00:37:14.780 line:80%
you kept digging in his hands.

00:37:19.100 --> 00:37:19.970 line:80%
You didn't come

00:37:20.660 --> 00:37:22.810 line:80%
for your son

00:37:23.810 --> 00:37:25.370 line:80%
but for the saliva.

00:37:26.220 --> 00:37:27.490 line:80%
That is Yulin's item.

00:37:27.660 --> 00:37:29.540 line:80%
Zhao, if I wanted to harm you,

00:37:29.850 --> 00:37:31.890 line:80%
why did I risk my life to protect you?

00:37:31.890 --> 00:37:33.290 line:80%
That was the reason

00:37:34.140 --> 00:37:35.450 line:80%
that I dismissed my doubts.

00:37:36.220 --> 00:37:37.580 line:80%
That's why I healed you.

00:37:37.740 --> 00:37:38.660 line:80%
Now, I see.

00:37:38.970 --> 00:37:40.740 line:80%
It was just a ruse.

00:37:41.370 --> 00:37:42.210 line:80%
Zhao,

00:37:42.780 --> 00:37:44.140 line:80%
we are both from the Six Sects.

00:37:44.140 --> 00:37:45.490 line:80%
I was friends with your aunt.

00:37:45.520 --> 00:37:46.370 line:80%
Why say this?

00:37:46.370 --> 00:37:47.660 line:80%
That's exactly why

00:37:47.660 --> 00:37:49.100 line:80%
I didn't want to believe it,

00:37:50.780 --> 00:37:51.930 line:80%
but just now,

00:37:52.740 --> 00:37:54.140 line:80%
I had no choice but to confirm.

00:37:55.410 --> 00:37:58.220 line:80%
You schemed for the saliva.

00:37:58.660 --> 00:38:00.450 line:80%
What exactly do you want with it?

00:38:03.993 --> 00:38:05.260 line:80%
Young lady, what are you doing?

00:38:05.260 --> 00:38:06.740 line:80%
I heard saliva melts in fire.

00:38:07.260 --> 00:38:08.220 line:80%
If Uncle Zhou

00:38:08.490 --> 00:38:09.580 line:80%
doesn't explain today,

00:38:10.140 --> 00:38:11.060 line:80%
I'll destroy it

00:38:12.260 --> 00:38:13.930 line:80%
to keep it from falling into evil hands.

00:38:15.370 --> 00:38:16.700 line:80%
Zhou Zhiqin, tell her!

00:38:18.930 --> 00:38:20.220 line:80%
I did it for Jianghu's safety,

00:38:20.780 --> 00:38:21.850 line:80%
bearing humiliation,

00:38:22.180 --> 00:38:23.850 line:80%
mingling with these demon sect people,

00:38:23.890 --> 00:38:25.536 line:80%
to prevent them
from practicing evil arts

00:38:26.176 --> 00:38:27.180 line:80%
and endangering everyone.

00:38:28.780 --> 00:38:29.620 line:80%
Evil arts?

00:38:30.010 --> 00:38:31.740 line:80%
It's called the Ziwei Method.

00:38:32.220 --> 00:38:33.450 line:80%
This method

00:38:33.450 --> 00:38:34.370 line:80%
was powerful

00:38:34.490 --> 00:38:35.370 line:80%
and invincible.

00:38:35.895 --> 00:38:37.362 line:80%
Later, Nie Hengcheng somehow acquired

00:38:37.373 --> 00:38:38.740 line:80%
its cultivation method,

00:38:39.100 --> 00:38:40.890 line:80%
and it became the root of all disasters.

00:38:41.490 --> 00:38:45.220 line:80%
So, practicing the Ziwei Method
needs the saliva.

00:38:47.620 --> 00:38:48.810 line:80%
What Ziwei Method?

00:38:49.330 --> 00:38:50.170 line:80%
I don't know.

00:38:50.970 --> 00:38:51.930 line:80%
Careful!

00:38:54.660 --> 00:38:55.780 line:80%
Did Zhou Zhiqin work with you

00:38:55.850 --> 00:38:57.060 line:80%
for the Ziwei Method?

00:39:03.100 --> 00:39:03.940 line:80%
Correct.

00:39:04.260 --> 00:39:05.780 line:80%
My master Nie Hengcheng

00:39:05.780 --> 00:39:08.410 line:80%
only reached the third layer

00:39:08.620 --> 00:39:09.930 line:80%
and was already invincible.

00:39:10.620 --> 00:39:12.410 line:80%
Mr. Zhou wants to practice it,

00:39:12.410 --> 00:39:14.890 line:80%
obviously to become
the Lord of Peiqiong Manor,

00:39:14.890 --> 00:39:17.580 line:80%
so he worked with Elder Tianji and me.

00:39:17.810 --> 00:39:18.850 line:80%
Is that right,

00:39:20.540 --> 00:39:21.410 line:80%
Mr. Zhou?

00:39:22.740 --> 00:39:24.700 line:80%
Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji

00:39:25.810 --> 00:39:27.490 line:80%
was already killed by my aunt.

00:39:27.740 --> 00:39:29.290 line:80%
Why is he still alive?

00:39:36.041 --> 00:39:46.701 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

